---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label">Collection note</p>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>A single car,<br /><em>carefully traced</em></h2>
        <p>
          This page follows one machine: Joe Petty&rsquo;s 1962 Lotus Super 7 (Series II),
          reconstructed from public USA7s posts. Joe is listed as a retired owner in
          Jacksonville, Florida, with documented activity from 2016 to 2025.
        </p>
        <p>
          Across those entries, the car appears as an ex-racer returned to regular use:
          wiring renewed, drivetrain and shifter details resolved, and period-correct parts
          sourced where possible. The emphasis is stewardship, not mythmaking.
        </p>
        <p>
          When posts conflict, or describe earlier configurations, details are marked
          unverified until current specification can be confirmed.
        </p>
      </div>
      <aside class="about-aside">
        <dl class="provenance">
          <div>
            <dt>Owner</dt>
            <dd>Joe Petty</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Car</dt>
            <dd>1962 Lotus Super 7 (S2)</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Location</dt>
            <dd>Jacksonville, Florida</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>USA7s member since</dt>
            <dd>June 16, 2016</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Public post count</dt>
            <dd>66</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Editorial note</dt>
            <dd>Some current-spec fields remain unverified</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--bg-section);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  h2 em {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .about-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-aside {
    align-self: start;
  }

  .provenance {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .provenance div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .provenance div:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .provenance dt {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .provenance dd {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
</style>
